summary: My Khajit save, in vanilla game, after civil war and right before.
descriptionHtml: I was going to start playing some of the DLC and was reminiscing on my old character and thought I'd share him. He's a sneaky sniper and always had a magic companion. I did alot of quest before finishing up the civil war, I don't know how many exactly. I also never killed Parthanax and finished Dark Brotherhood.
author: durog79
